                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for gmahajan &amp;lt;gmahajan@ddn.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;http://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/10687878-f427-11e2-b8a2-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/10687878-f427-11e2-b8a2-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_20b failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;test_20b failed with 3&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;client log:&lt;/p&gt;
